{
  "chapter": 7,
  "chapter_summary": "白万剑率雪山派众人闯入长乐帮，当众擒住石破天并挟持突围，贝海石虽击倒大批雪山弟子，却仍被白万剑带人逃脱。白万剑在土地庙中部署撤返凌霄城，又借众弟子拆招之机剖析雪山剑法精微，石破天旁观之下竟暗自记住大半。其后石清、闵柔追至，与白万剑激斗，闵柔更以柔和心意暗中教石破天喂招。石破天凭深厚内力初次使出雪山剑法，震断石清长剑，却在黑暗中误被闵柔刺伤。白万剑再度以他为质逼退石清夫妇，待欲点灯善后时，却发现石破天已神秘失踪。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_chong_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "陈冲之",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "帮主，不必跟他们多说，以武力决是非。胜的便对，败的便错。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "speaker_name": "白万剑",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "石中玉听了：白万剑奉本派掌门人威德先生令谕，今日清理门户。这是雪山派本门之事，与旁人无涉。若在长乐帮总舵动手不便，咱们到外边了断如何？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 9,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "text": "了……了什么断？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 13,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_dang",
      "speaker_name": "丁珰",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "跟他打啊，你武功比他强得多，杀了他便是。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 13,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_ding_dang",
      "text": "我……我不杀他，为什么要杀他？白师傅又不是坏人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 15,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "speaker_name": "白万剑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "列位朋友，今日得罪了，日后登门赔礼！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 31,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_chong_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "陈冲之",
      "listener": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "text": "放下帮主！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 35,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "speaker_name": "白万剑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那一个上来，兄弟只得先毙了石中玉，再和各位周旋。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bei_hai_shi",
      "speaker_name": "贝海石",
      "listener": "char_ke_wan_jun",
      "text": "柯朋友不用性急，待小弟叫人开门送客。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wan_zi",
      "speaker_name": "花万紫",
      "listener": "char_bei_hai_shi",
      "text": "退开了！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "speaker_name": "白万剑",
      "listener": "char_bei_hai_shi",
      "text": "好功夫，好五行六合掌，姓白的改日定要领教！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bei_hai_shi",
      "speaker_name": "贝海石",
      "listener": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "text": "何不今日领教？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 65,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bu_san",
      "speaker_name": "丁不三",
      "listener": "char_ding_dang",
      "text": "不忙！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chuan_jia",
      "speaker_name": "船家",
      "listener": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "text": "多谢客官厚赏，只是小人的船小，经不起江中风浪，靠着岸驶，勉强还能对付。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 121,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "speaker_name": "白万剑",
      "listener": "char_chuan_jia",
      "text": "靠南岸顺流而下最好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "speaker_name": "白万剑",
      "listener": "char_xue_shan_di_zi_men",
      "text": "众位师弟，愚兄侥幸得手，终于擒到了这罪魁祸首。大家难道不认得他了？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nian_zhang_di_zi",
      "speaker_name": "年长弟子",
      "listener": "char_xue_shan_di_zi_men",
      "text": "大家可莫打伤了他。白师哥马到功成，可喜，可贺。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 137,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "speaker_name": "白万剑",
      "listener": "char_nian_zhang_di_zi",
      "text": "虽然擒得这小子，却失陷了七位师弟、师妹，其实是得不偿失。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "speaker_name": "白万剑",
      "listener": "char_xue_shan_di_zi_men",
      "text": "咱们须得尽快将这小子送往凌霄城，去交由掌门人发落。七位师弟、师妹虽然陷敌，谅来长乐帮想到帮主在咱们手中，也不敢难为他们。张师弟、钱师弟、赵师弟三位是南方人，留在镇江城中，乔装改扮了，打探讯息。好在你们没跟长乐帮朝过相，他们认不出来。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 151,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "speaker_name": "白万剑",
      "listener": "char_zhang_qian_zhao_san_ren",
      "text": "汪万翼汪师弟机灵多智，你们三个和他联络上后，全听他吩咐。可别自以为入门早过他，摆师兄的架子，坏了大事。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "speaker_name": "白万剑",
      "listener": "char_xue_shan_di_zi_men",
      "text": "咱们在这里等到天黑，东下到常州申浦再过长江，远兜圈子回凌霄城去。路程虽远些，长乐帮却决计料不到咱们会走这条路。这时候他们一定都已追过江北去了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "speaker_name": "白万剑",
      "listener": "char_xue_shan_di_zi_men",
      "text": "咱们这次来到中原，虽然烧了玄素庄，擒得逆徒石中玉，但孙、褚两位师弟死于非命，耿师弟他们又陷于敌手，实大折本派的锐气，归根结底，总是愚兄统率无方。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_yan_wan_shan",
      "speaker_name": "呼延万善",
      "listener": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "text": "白师哥不必自责，其实真正原因，还是众兄弟武功没练得到家。大伙儿一般受师父传授，可是本门中除白师哥、封师哥两位之外，都只学了师尊武学的一点儿皮毛，没学到师门功夫的精义。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_wan_fu",
      "speaker_name": "闻万夫",
      "listener": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "text": "咱们在凌霄城中自己较量，都自以为了不起啦，不料到得外面来，才知满不是这么一回事。白师哥，咱们要等到天黑才动身，左右无事，请你指点大伙儿几招。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "speaker_name": "白万剑",
      "listener": "char_xue_shan_di_zi_men",
      "text": "爹爹传授众兄弟的武功，全然一模一样，不存半分偏私。你们瞧，封师哥练功比我勤勉，他功夫便在我之上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_wan_fu",
      "speaker_name": "闻万夫",
      "listener": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "text": "师父绝无偏私，这是人人知道的，只恨做兄弟的太蠢，领会不到其中诀窍。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "speaker_name": "白万剑",
      "listener": "char_hu_yan_wan_shan",
      "text": "此去凌霄城，途中未必太平无事，多学一招剑法，咱们的力量便增了一分。呼延师弟、闻师弟，你们两个便过过招。赵师弟、钱师弟，你们到外边守望，见到有甚动静，立即传声通报。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_wan_fu",
      "speaker_name": "闻万夫",
      "listener": "char_hu_yan_wan_shan",
      "text": "呼延师哥请！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_yan_wan_shan",
      "speaker_name": "呼延万善",
      "listener": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "text": "请白师哥点拨。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "speaker_name": "白万剑",
      "listener": "char_xue_shan_di_zi_men",
      "text": "且住！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "speaker_name": "白万剑",
      "listener": "char_hu_yan_wan_shan",
      "text": "这一招只须再向前递得两寸，便已胜了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_yan_wan_shan",
      "speaker_name": "呼延万善",
      "listener": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "text": "白师哥指教得是，只小弟这一招“风沙莽莽”使到这里，内力已尽，再也没法刺前半寸。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "speaker_name": "白万剑",
      "listener": "char_xue_shan_di_zi_men",
      "text": "内力修为，原非一朝一夕之功。但内力不足，可用剑法上的变化补救。本派的内功秘诀，老实说未必有特别的过人之处，比之少林、武当、峨嵋、昆仑诸派，虽说各有所长，毕竟雪山一派创派的年月尚短，可能还不足以与已有数百年积累的诸大派相较。但本派剑法之奇，实说得上海内无双。诸位师弟在临敌之际，便须以我之长，攻敌之短，不可与人比拚内力，力求以剑招之变化精微取胜。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "speaker_name": "白万剑",
      "listener": "char_xue_shan_di_zi_men",
      "text": "这小子入我门来，短短两三年内，便领悟到本派武功精要之所在，比之学了十年、二十年的许多师伯、师叔，招式之纯自然不如，机变却大有过之。本派剑法原以轻灵变化为尚，有此门徒，封师哥固然甚为得意，掌门人对他也青眼有加，期许他光大本派。唉……唉……唉……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "speaker_name": "白万剑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "何方高人降临？便请下来一叙如何？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "speaker_name": "白万剑",
      "listener": "char_shi_qing",
      "text": "原来是玄素庄石庄主夫妇驾到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing",
      "speaker_name": "石清",
      "listener": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "text": "白万剑，你雪山派欺人太甚。石某夫妇今日既然追到这里，总要领回犬子。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_min_rou",
      "speaker_name": "闵柔",
      "listener": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "text": "我儿纵有不是，也轮不到你们将他擒去处置。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "speaker_name": "白万剑",
      "listener": "char_shi_qing",
      "text": "石中玉辱我爱女，罪证确凿。两位若讲武林规矩，便不该再来阻挠。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 271,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing",
      "speaker_name": "石清",
      "listener": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "text": "我夫妇若再妄自尊大，以为我石清便不如你白万剑了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing",
      "speaker_name": "石清",
      "listener": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "text": "好剑法！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "speaker_name": "白万剑",
      "listener": "char_shi_qing",
      "text": "此是石庄主剑质较劣，并非剑招上分了输赢。石庄主若有黑剑在手，宝剑焉能折断？倒是兄弟的不是了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "speaker_name": "白万剑",
      "listener": "char_shi_qing",
      "text": "只可惜封师哥不在这里，否则封白二人联手，当可和贤伉俪较量一场。今日败势已成，还有什么可说？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们少了一个人，比不成剑，我来跟白师傅联手，凑个兴儿。不过我是不会的，请你们指点。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 343,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_min_rou",
      "speaker_name": "闵柔",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "玉……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 349,
      "line_end": 349
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "speaker_name": "白万剑",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "你为什么要和我联剑？要试试你在雪山派所学的剑法？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 355,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "text": "我学的也不知学对了没有，请白师傅和石庄主、石夫人教我。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 357,
      "line_end": 357
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_min_rou",
      "speaker_name": "闵柔",
      "listener": "char_shi_qing",
      "text": "好啊，咱们四个便二对二的研讨一下武功，反正是点到为止，也没什么相干。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "speaker_name": "白万剑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是二对二也好，是三对一也好，白某人反正是玄素双剑的手下败将，再来舍命陪君子便是。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 373
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么是由我抢攻了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 375,
      "line_end": 375
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_shi_qing",
      "text": "啊哟！",
