    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing",
      "speaker_name": "石清",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "不用顾忌，接招罢！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_min_rou",
      "speaker_name": "闵柔",
      "listener": "char_shi_qing",
      "text": "师哥！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 395,
      "line_end": 395
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_shi_qing",
      "text": "多谢你手下留情，我的剑法学得全然不对，比你可差得远了！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing",
      "speaker_name": "石清",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来来来，大家不用有什么顾忌，好好的比剑。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_min_rou",
      "speaker_name": "闵柔",
      "listener": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "text": "刺伤了你吗？伤在那里？伤在那里？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 433,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_po_tian",
      "speaker_name": "石破天",
      "listener": "char_min_rou",
      "text": "我……我……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_min_rou",
      "speaker_name": "闵柔",
      "listener": "char_shi_qing",
      "text": "师哥，怎……怎么办？",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "speaker_name": "白万剑",
      "listener": "char_shi_qing",
      "text": "令郎辱我爱女，累得她小小年纪，投崖自尽，此仇不能不报。两位要是容我带他上凌霄城去，至少尚有二月之命，但若欲用强，我这一剑便刺下去了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "speaker_name": "白万剑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有鬼，有鬼！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_wan_jian",
      "speaker_name": "白万剑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "鬼鬼祟祟的不是好汉，出来决个死战。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
